  <brief_title>Trial With Bronchipret and Sinupret to Evaluate Acceleration of Mucociliary Clearance (MCC)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized, Placebo-controlled, Double-blind, Cross-over Trial With Bronchipret and Sinupret to Evaluate Acceleration of Mucociliary Clearance (MCC)</official_title>
